====跳躍搬運====
地質上的[[跳躍_(地質學)|跳躍]]作用是重要的增加火星大氣層內粒子過程。跳躍的砂礫已經被精神號火星車觀察到<ref>G. Landis, et al., "Dust and Sand Deposition on the MER Solar Arrays as Viewed by the Microscopic Imager," 37th Lunar and Planetary Science Conference, Houston TX, March 13–17, 2006. [http://www.lpi.usra.edu/meetings/lpsc2006/pdf/1932.pdf pdf file] {{Wayback|url=http://www.lpi.usra.edu/meetings/lpsc2006/pdf/1932.pdf |date=20081201152947 }} (also summarized in NASA Glenn [http://www.grc.nasa.gov/WWW/RT/2006/RP/RPV-landis2.html Research and Technology 2006] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090510064530/http://www.grc.nasa.gov/WWW/RT/2006/RP/RPV-landis2.html |date=2009-05-10 }} report</ref>。理論和實際觀察目前仍互相不符合，古典理論忽略了一半真實狀況跳躍作用中的粒子<ref>{{cite journal |last=Kok |first=Jasper F. |authorlink= |coauthors=Renno, Nilton O. |year=2008 |month= |title= Electrostatics in Wind-Blown Sand |journal=[[物理评论快报|Physical Review Letters]] |volume=100 |issue= 1|pages=014501 |doi=10.1103/PhysRevLett.100.014501 |url= |accessdate= |quote= |pmid=18232774 |bibcode=2008PhRvL.100a4501K}}</ref>。一個新的模型更加密切符合實際觀察，並表明跳躍粒子產生了增加跳躍效果的電場。火星粒子跳躍的高度和長度超過地球上相當直徑粒子的100倍，而速度是5到10倍<ref>{{cite journal |last=Almeida |first=Murilo P. |authorlink=  |year=2008 |month= |title=Giant saltation on Mars |journal=[[美國國家科學院院刊|PNAS]] |volume=105 |issue= 17|pages=6222–6226 |doi=10.1073/pnas.0800202105 |url= |accessdate= |quote= |pmid=18443302 |pmc=2359785 |bibcode = 2008PNAS..105.6222A |display-authors=1 |last2=Parteli |first2=E. J. R. |last3=Andrade |first3=J. S. |last4=Herrmann |first4=H. J. }}</ref>

===氣旋風暴===
[[Image:Mars_cyclone.jpg|thumb]]
在海盜號軌道探測器首先對火星表面進行測繪後，許多探測器和望遠鏡都發現了類似颶風的氣旋風暴。影像顯示這些氣旋是白色的，與更常見的沙塵暴不同。這些風暴傾向在火星北半球的夏季出現，且都位於高緯度區。推測這是因為火星北極點附近的獨特氣候環境造成<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.news.cornell.edu/releases/May99/mars.cyclone.deb.html | title=Colossal cyclone swirling near Martian north pole is observed by Cornell-led team on Hubble telescope | publisher=Cornell News | author=David Brand and Ray Villard | date=19 May 1999 | accessdate=2007-09-06 | archive-date=2012-08-05 | archive-url=https://archive.today/20120805123312/http://www.news.cornell.edu/releases/May99/mars.cyclone.deb.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===甲烷的存在===
[[ESA|ESA]]的[[火星快車號|火星快車號]]已經在火星大氣層中發現[[甲烷|甲烷]]，含量大約是10 nL/L<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.astronomy.com/asy/default.aspx?c=a&id=4009 | publisher=Astronomy Magazine | title=Titan, Mars methane may be on ice | author=Francis Reddy | date=7 March 2006 | accessdate=2007-09-06 | archive-date=2007-09-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070927214224/http://www.astronomy.com/asy/default.aspx?c=a&id=4009 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="methane-me">{{cite journal | author= V. Formisano, S. Atreya, T. Encrenaz, N. Ignatiev, M. Giuranna | title= Detection of Methane in the Atmosphere of Mars | journal = [[科学_(期刊)|Science]] | year= 2004 | volume= 306 | pages= 1758–1761 |doi= 10.1126/science.1101732 | pmid= 15514118 | issue= 5702|bibcode = 2004Sci...306.1758F }}
</ref><ref name="methane">{{cite news | date = March 30, 2004 | title = Mars Express confirms methane in the Martian atmosphere | publisher = [[ESA|ESA]] | url = http://www.esa.int/SPECIALS/Mars_Express/SEMZ0B57ESD_0.html | accessdate = 2008-08-19 | archive-date = 2006-02-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20060224102528/http://www.esa.int/SPECIALS/Mars_Express/SEMZ0B57ESD_0.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。因為[[紫外線|紫外線]]會分解甲烷，以目前火星大氣層的狀況應只能存在350年，因此必須有某種來源補充甲烷
<ref>{{cite journal | author=Martin Baucom | title=Life on Mars? | journal=American Scientist | year=2006 | volume=94 | issue=2 | url=http://www.americanscientist.org/template/AssetDetail/assetid/49613 | accessdate=2007-02-26 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060223045353/http://www.americanscientist.org/template/AssetDetail/assetid/49613 | archivedate=2006年2月23日 | deadurl=yes }}</ref>。火星目前的氣候狀況可能破壞[[籠狀水合物|籠狀水合物]]，但目前對火星甲烷的來源仍無共識。

===二氧化碳的侵蝕===
[[火星侦察轨道器|火星侦察轨道器]]拍攝影像中顯示了一個基於火星特殊氣候下的特別侵蝕作用。春季在特定區域溫度上升造成二氧化碳昇華和向上流動，造成稱為「火星蜘蛛」的特殊侵蝕模式<ref name="nyt20071212">{{cite news | url=http://www.nytimes.com/2007/12/12/science/space/12mars.html?ex=1355202000&en=c42725b421422007&ei=5124&partner=permalink&exprod=permalink | work=The New York Times | title=Mars Rover Finding Suggests Once Habitable Environment | first=Kenneth | last=Chang | date=2007-12-12 | accessdate=2010-04-30 | archive-date=2009-03-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090316085348/http://www.nytimes.com/2007/12/12/science/space/12mars.html?ex=1355202000&en=c42725b421422007&ei=5124&partner=permalink&exprod=permalink | dead-url=no }}</ref>。半透明乾冰在冬季形成，當春季太陽能量使其表面溫度上升時會使二氧化碳昇華成氣體，並在半透明的乾冰下流動，遇到乾冰層弱點時就會噴發形成噴泉<ref name="nyt20071212"/>。

==山嶽==
火星的風暴明顯受到火星上大規模的山地影響<ref>{{cite web | title=The Martian mountain ranges... | author=[[火星大氣環流模式|Mars General Circulation Model]]ing Group | publisher=[[NASA|NASA]] | url=http://www-mgcm.arc.nasa.gov/mgcm/HTML/WEATHER/mountains.html | accessdate=2007-09-08 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070707084816/http://www-mgcm.arc.nasa.gov/mgcm/HTML/WEATHER/mountains.html | archivedate=2007-07-07 }}
</ref>，[[奧林帕斯山_(火星)|奧林帕斯山]]等[[火星山列表|個別的山峰]]可以影響區域天氣，但是塔爾西斯的火山群可以大範圍影響火星天氣。

一個涉及山地的天氣重複現象是位於[[阿爾西亞山|阿爾西亞山]]上方的螺旋狀塵埃雲。該螺旋狀塵埃雲覆蓋阿爾西亞山，高度約15到30公里<ref>{{cite web | url=http://photojournal.jpl.nasa.gov/catalog/PIA04294 | title=PIA04294: Repeated Clouds over Arsia Mons | publisher=[[NASA|NASA]] | accessdate=2007-09-08 | archive-date=2017-02-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170212193056/http://photojournal.jpl.nasa.gov/catalog/PIA04294/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。在整個火星年這些雲都出現在阿爾西亞山周圍，在夏末達到最高峰<ref name=icarus>{{cite journal|journal=[[伊卡洛斯_(期刊)|Icarus]]|title=Interannual variability of water ice clouds over major martian volcanoes observed by MOC|year=2006|author=Benson|volume=184|pages=365–371|doi=10.1016/j.icarus.2006.03.014|last2=James|first2=P|last3=Cantor|first3=B|last4=Remigio|first4=R|bibcode=2006Icar..184..365B|display-authors=1|issue=2}}</ref>。

雲周圍的群山顯示了季節性變化。奧林帕斯山和[[艾斯克雷爾斯山|艾斯克雷爾斯山]]周圍的雲在北半球春季和夏季覆蓋面積達到最大，在晚春時面積分別是大約 900,000 km<sup>2</sup>和1,000,000 km<sup>2</sup>。[[亞拔山|亞拔山]]和[[帕弗尼斯山|帕弗尼斯山]]周圍的雲量在夏末有一個額外的小高峰。在冬季非常少雲被觀測到，而火星大氣環流模式的預測和觀測結果相一致<ref name=icarus />。

==極冠==
